I've got spots in my eyes.

476
00:41:25,810 --> 00:41:28,470
别这样，艾迪
Stop it, Eddie.

477
00:41:29,450 --> 00:41:32,820
- 谢谢了，维基 - 谢谢，夜枭先生
- Thank you, Weegee. - Thank you, Mr. Owl.

478
00:41:34,020 --> 00:41:37,220
明天，3点，我的工作室
Tomorrow, 3:00, my studio.

479
00:41:37,390 --> 00:41:40,550
