I know what you need.

487
00:42:21,100 --> 00:42:25,160
你把衣服设计成这样，肯定有原因的
You gotta have some kind of reason for dressing in an outfit like this.

488
00:42:25,340 --> 00:42:27,640
我说不要，艾迪
I said no, Eddie.

489
00:42:28,270 --> 00:42:33,180
- 不要就是要 - 不要就是不要
- No spelled Y-E-S. - No spelled N-O.

490
00:42:33,350 --> 00:42:36,780
- 别这样 - 来吧，宝贝
