Of course, they're not famous, are they?

1350
01:53:30,840 --> 01:53:33,530
你想了解罗夏？
You wanna know about Rorschach?

1351
01:53:35,010 --> 01:53:36,770
我来跟你说说罗夏
I'll tell you about Rorschach.

1352
01:53:38,080 --> 01:53:40,570
