...that it doesn't exist, no matter who orders him to look the other way.

1356
01:53:50,920 --> 01:53:54,480
我们不会那样
We don't do this thing...

1357
01:53:54,660 --> 01:53:56,750
因为我们是正义的
...because it's permitted.

1358
01:53:57,400 --> 01:53:59,960
我们必须那么做
We do it because we have to.

1359
01:54:00,700 --> 01:54:02,960
我们被自己强迫那么做
We do it because we're compelled.

1360
01:54:04,800 --> 01:54:07,240
那时候我正在调查一项绑架案
I was investigating a kidnap case.

1361
01:54:08,970 --> 01:54:10,840
布莱尔·罗切
Blaire Roche.

1362
01:54:11,010 --> 01:54:14,440
一个6岁的女孩，当时我还年轻
Six-year-old girl. I was young then.

1363
01:54:15,310 --> 01:54:17,650
对罪犯比较手软
Too soft on criminals.

1364
01:54:18,580 --> 01:54:20,210
不会杀掉他们
I let them live.

1365
01:54:21,490 --> 01:54:27,220
打断了一个人的手之后我得到了线索 来到了失踪女孩的位置
Broke a man's arm to get a tip. Led me to the missing girl's location.

1366
01:54:34,830 --> 01:54:37,270
我觉得女孩应该在这儿
I knew the girl was here...

1367
01:54:37,440 --> 01:54:40,960
不过搜索之后，什么也没找到
... but when I searched the place, I saw nothing.

1368
01:54:41,840 --> 01:54:44,270
然后我看到了她
And then I found her.

1369
01:55:33,620 --> 01:55:35,490
弗雷德
MAN: Fred.

1370
01:55:36,360 --> 01:55:38,190
巴尼
Barney.

1371
01:55:38,360 --> 01:55:41,090
谁给老爸叫两声听听？
Who's gonna bark for Daddy?

1372
01:55:46,540 --> 01:55:49,800
犯人回来的时候，天已经黑了
It was dark when the murderer got back.

1373
01:55:51,540 --> 01:55:53,130
一片漆黑
As dark as it gets.

1374
01:56:31,780 --> 01:56:36,650
